rows.label: tlk70000050_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Phew, if you hadn't shown up that
time to help, I'd still be up to my
neck in Parisax bits, I tell you!

rows.label: tlk70000050_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Those damn bugs have such a good
sense of smell, they always sniff
out food. Audacious bastards.

rows.label: tlk70000050_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Anyway, I'm glad that's all over!
Now that the stress is gone, I'm
starting to get hungry.

rows.label: tlk70000050_04_msg0004
rows.name:
What do you mean it's too
early for food? It might
be with that attitude!

rows.label: tlk70000050_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Hahaha, I'm just kidding! Of course I'm
not in the habit of snacking or anything
like that. Don't be silly. *Urp*
